ls that are good for you and the environment, focusing on natural, renewable, and recycled resources. Join us in making conscious choices for a healthier planet.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\" style=\"margin-top: 40px; text-align: center;\">\n            <h2>Get in Touch</h2>\n            <p>Email: info@ecolivinghome.com</p>\n            <p>Follow us on social media!</p>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 EcoLiving Home. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}